## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="97cfe-123">L’exemple suivant effectue la reconnaissance vocale asynchrone sur une grammaire de reconnaissance vocale, à l’aide de la <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine.RecognizeAsync%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> méthode avec le module de reconnaissance en cours.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="97cfe-123">The following example performs asynchronous speech recognition on a speech recognition grammar, using the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine.RecognizeAsync%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> method with the in-process recognizer.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="97cfe-124">L’exemple utilise <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Choices> et <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder> objets pour créer la grammaire de reconnaissance vocale avant de générer dans un <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Grammar> objet.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="97cfe-124">The example uses <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Choices> and <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder> objects to create the speech recognition grammar before building it into a <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Grammar> object.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="97cfe-125">Un gestionnaire pour le <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine.RecognizeCompleted?displayProperty=nameWithType> événements génère des informations sur l’opération de reconnaissance à la console.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="97cfe-125">A handler for the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine.RecognizeCompleted?displayProperty=nameWithType> event outputs information about the recognition operation to the console.</span></span>  
  
